Usage: set_model_priority [-help] [-objects <string>] [-priority_list <string>]

-help                       # Prints out the command usage
-objects <string>           # list of lib_cells/lib_pins for which priority is
                            # specified (string, optional)
-priority_list <string>     # list of pin model priority, default = {ecsm ccs
                            # nldm cdb udn} (string, optional)